sourcesContent: import React from "react"; import { Button } from "../ButtonElements"; import { InfoContainer, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Column1, Column2, TextWrapper, TopLine, Subtitle, Heading, Btnwrap, Img, ImgWrapper, } from "./infoElements"; const infoSection = ({ lightBackground, id, imgStart, lightText, topLine, headLine, description, buttonLabel, img, alt, dark, primary, darkText, }) => { return ( <> {topLine} {headLine} {description} ); }; export default infoSection;
